Arthur J. Gallagher & Co., the
fourth-largest insurance broker, agreed to buy Risk Planners
Inc. to increase its commercial insurance coverage for the
retail grocery industry.  Risk Planners, based in  Eden Prairie ,  Minnesota , will
operate under Thomas J. Gallagher, midwest regional manager of
the retail property and casualty brokerage operation, Itasca,
Illinois-based Gallagher said today in a PR Newswire statement
